## Core Principle

**Client requirement:** "Negro el fondo y uno o dos colores" — "fondo negro y como un color medio neón". **Important color:** Celeste neónsito (primary color for landing).

The design system is structured with a **primary color group** centralized in `app/globals.css` to facilitate constant color modifications.

