## Web Adaptation

### Design Tokens
- Tokens in `app/globals.css` (variables `--color-*`, `--font-*`) and Tailwind `@theme`.
- Fonts via `next/font/google`; alternatives for Palatino/Lovelo if not available (Cormorant/Lora, Exo 2/Nunito).
- Use utility classes `font-logo`, `font-title`, `font-subtitle`, `font-body` and color utilities (`bg-primary`, `text-primary`, etc.).

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Use responsive prefixes: `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`
- Adjust text sizes responsively: `text-5xl md:text-8xl`

### Accessibility
- Maintain proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)
- Ensure keyboard navigation works
- Provide alt text for images
- Ensure color contrast ratios meet WCAG standards
- Use ARIA labels when needed
- Test with screen readers

### Selection
- Use primary color (celeste neónsito) for `::selection` background.

