## Component Usage Guidelines

### Buttons
- **Primary CTA:** Solid primary color background with white text, rounded corners.
- **Secondary/Outline:** Transparent background with primary color border and white/primary text, rounded corners.

### Cards/Panels
- Dark background (black or `--color-bg-secondary` if subtle contrast needed), rounded corners.
- Primary color borders or glows for emphasis.
- White titles, light gray body text.

### Navigation
- Minimalist top navigation with white text links and primary color CTA button.

### Icons
- Simple, line-art or glyph-based icons, usually white or primary color.
- Sometimes within glowing circular or square backgrounds using primary color.

